skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: This daily briefing includes detailed events and descriptions about upcoming and the latest games, events, and technology. Everything you need to know at the beginning of your morning or end of a long day to keep you up to date.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
